task.summary: Make registry an observer and TCPReceiver observable. Multiple nodes can now connect to registry.
Create connectionList in nodes for outgoing communications.
Messaging nodes can now register and deregister with the registry.
Make Node an abstract class and nix onEvent for Observer.update.
Messaging Nodes can connect to one another.
Link weights assigned during overlay setup and can be sent to messaging nodes.
Nodes can send and receive messages but some disappear.
Nodes can properly connect and send messages to all neighbors.
Nodes are properly tracking send an receive counts when sending to random neighbors.
Registry properly receives and displays summary for 10 nodes each sending 125000 messages.
Add Dijkstra classes. Clean up output. Remove lots of print statements.
Dijkstra implemented but not working properly
Let's see how bad these bugs are.
